{
  "stem": "4570.3",
  "chunk_idx": 0,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 7.5,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "I came to Auschwitz in-- I wouldn't know exact date, but in September, 1944.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And I must have been there about six weeks all together.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And because there was such an influx when I came to Auschwitz, I never got a number, which I would like to have.",
      "word_count": 23
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "I was never tattooed.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Well, it was utterly, utterly unreal.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "It is like if you see a spooky movie, and, and, and I had the feeling at times that I'm just looking in, that it is not happening, that it is a nightmare or, or, or, or some movie or-- it was just so utterly, utterly unreal.",
      "word_count": 47
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "Because the people-- I mean, all the time somebody came into the barracks, and we had to strip naked, and we had to stand for hours naked, and the band was going around playing.",
      "word_count": 34
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And when we went to the latrines, the, the guys that were supposed to be murderers-- because we were told if it's a, a, a red triangle or whatever-- so they were in charge of us.",
      "word_count": 36
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And there we were sitting on the latrines with the maggots in, in-- lower-- ugh.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "Looking down at the maggots, I mean, you know, you always were like, I hope I won't fall in.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "And there you sat once a day.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "And you had ten women in front of you saying, hurry up, hurry up.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "And then the, the guy who is the murderer in his pajama with a long, long whip, was running around whipping us so that we-- whatever we had to do, we'd do it quicker.",
      "word_count": 34
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "I mean, it, it was just totally nutty.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "It was totally-- I think the only thing they had organized well was the killing machine.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "Otherwise, it just nothing made sense in that place.",
      "word_count": 9
    }
  ],
